title: 10 year annie versery summoners icon
body: i got the skin but not the icon.. i want the icon.. can rito look into my account for me???

replies.body: What Lew suggested is on point.  All the gifts are still being sent out, and you may not get everything all at once.  Stay updated on our [support ticket](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/requests/new) as we continue to send out gifts.  Hang tight!
The gifts are all rolling out individually and you should have everything by 9/23.
